# .gitignore for papers/tf_systems
#
# paper/ tracks the LaTeX source, the compiled PDF, figures/, and the SIAM class
# file siamonline250211.cls (committed on the author's decision, 16 July 2026, so
# the paper folder is self-contained and `make paper` works from a fresh clone).

# LaTeX build artifacts (the PDF is TRACKED)
paper/*.aux
paper/*.log
paper/*.out
paper/*.synctex.gz
paper/*.toc


# regenerated intermediates that are not the committed caches
replication/results/*.out

# python
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc

# local notes and reviews, never published
private/
